node.name: Blockchain-Voting-System
node.description: The Block Chain Based Voting system is a project created by Blocksmiths team, In this project we used solidty to create the smart contract and hosted it on Ganache, (you can also deploy the contract on public ethereum ledger) .The frontend DApp is developed using Reactjs and integrated with the smart contract using Web3.js

node.name: Static-code-analyzer
node.description: Static Code Analysis is a method of analyzing the source code of programs without running them. It can discover formatting problems, null pointer dereferencing, and other simple scenarios.

node.name: static-code-analyzer-webservice
node.description: The static-code-analyser-webservice is a gating service (used for java projects), which is used to check if a project passes the thresholds for different kinds of code analysis, which can be set by the user.

node.name: WeatherApplication
node.description: This application is used to display the weather of a particular city. Users have the flexibility to add the new city to monitor the weather.
